title: 01/20/22 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 01/20/22 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to NBC's Chris Simms about the possibility of Jim Harbaugh coming back to the NFL. ESPN's Booger McFarland tells us who he thinks is the best QB remaining in the Playoffs. And Lakers writer Bill Oram tells us what changes could be coming for the Lakers.
